.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-8::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain, bongani, tiparillo, havana, swisher
1. the bongani-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
2. the havana-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Cigar   | chaman | havana | cain | bongani | swisher | tiparillo |

