.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-9::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: green, brown, apricot, blood-red, ebony, white
1. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes white##2
2. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes green##2
3. the person who likes white is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes apricot##2
4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |        2        |   3    |    4     |  5   |     6     |
| Color   | blood-red | ebony | white | apricot | brown | green |

