.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-12::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, snowmobile, skateboard, helicopter, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the helicopter##2
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |  2  |   3   |   4    |  5   |   6    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | helicopter | trike | snowmobile | skateboard | ship |

