.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-15::.
There 6 different types of food: asparagus, papaya, banana, mango, lime, raspberry
1. the person eating banana is the person eating banana##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating banana##1
3. the person eating lime is between the person eating mango and the person eating asparagus##2
4. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |
| Food   | raspberry | papaya | banana | asparagus | lime | mango |

